口述实录｜确诊病例的小区怎么消毒？来看看卫生消杀员的十二时辰。
Oral record: How to disinfect the district where the case was confirmed? Come to see the twelve hours of the sanitary disinfector.
陶贵永、阿布。
Tao Guiyong, Abu.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
新民周刊。
Xinmin Weekly.
深度和角度——这就是我们能做的。
Depth and angle - that's what we can do.
。
.
编者按：新冠病毒封住了大家的脚步，闷在家里做贡献，成了上海人的日常；而有那么一群人，却每天都要走街串巷，越是容易传播病毒的地方，越是普通人避之唯恐不及的地方，越要往里冲——陶贵永就是其中之一，他们是城市里的“逆行者”——专业卫生消杀人员。
Editor's Note: The New Crown Virus has blocked everyone's step and made contributions at home, a daily routine for Shanghainese. But there is a group of people who travel the streets every day, spread the virus more easily, and rush inwards the more people avoid places they fear - Tao Guiyong is one of them, they are the city's "insiders" - professional health workers.
口述 | 陶贵永整理 | 阿　布我叫陶贵永，是长宁区新华街道爱国卫生服务社的专业卫生消杀员。
My name is Tao Guiyong, a professional sanitary cleaner at Xinhua Street Patriotic Health Service in Changning.
在没有突发疫情的时候，我们的工作主要是除四害和病媒防制，说得简单通俗一点——春秋天要去食堂饭店灭老鼠，夏天要喷洒药水灭蚊蝇。
In the absence of a sudden outbreak of disease, our work is mainly to eliminate four hazards and vector control, to put it simply - in the spring and autumn to the canteen restaurants to kill rats, summer spray to kill mosquitoes.
我从事病媒防制工作已经8年了，做我们这一行需要人社部颁发的专业证书，分初级、中级和高级，每一级都需要经过专门学校的培训、考试，还需要一定的工作年限，我目前是高级职称。
I have been working in the field of vector control for eight years, and I need a professional certificate from the Ministry of Health for my profession, at the primary, intermediate and advanced levels, each of which requires specialized school training, examinations and a certain number of years of service.
正是因为受过专业的训练，我们很清楚针对不同的疫情需要不同的消杀方案——比如说登革热疫情，涉及面积更大，确诊病例的直径200米范围内都是重点消杀区域；而新冠病毒影响范围相对小，发现病例的话，需要对整栋楼进行重点消杀。
Because of professional training, we know that different outbreaks require different killing regimens - dengue fever, for example, in larger areas, with priority elimination areas within 200 metres of the diameter of confirmed cases; and the new crown virus, which affects a relatively small area, requires focused elimination of the entire building if a case is found.
不同疫情配备不同的预案、不同的流程，我们平时就很熟悉了，所以这次疫情一来，马上就做好了应急预案。
Different epidemic situation equipped with different plans, different processes, we are usually familiar with, so this outbreak, immediately made a contingency plan.
前几天我们接到街道的通知，法华镇路某小区发现一名确诊病例。
A few days ago we received a street notice that a confirmed case was found in a small area of Fahuazhen Road.
等病人送往医院后，我们马上赶到现场——病人家属正在收拾行李准备搬去别的地方隔离，凡是他们带走的衣物、用品、车辆我们都要进行消毒，人离开以后，对病人居住过的房子也进行消毒。
As soon as the patient was taken to the hospital, we rushed to the scene - the family was packing up and moving to another area to be quarantined. We had to disinfect all the clothes, articles, and vehicles they had taken with them, as well as the house where the patient lived.
到了现场我发现，这是一栋26层的电梯房，我心想这下任务重了——从大堂到顶楼，每一层的楼道、电梯间、公共部位都要进行喷洒消毒，背着40斤的消毒桶一层一层爬上去，一层一层喷……从下午4点左右一直忙到夜里11点钟，浑身湿透，口罩摘下来都能甩出水。
On arriving at the scene, I found that it was a 26-story elevator house, and I thought it was a heavy task - spraying the aisles, elevator rooms, and public areas on every floor from the lobby to the top, with 40 kilos of disinfectant buckets on each floor, one layer at a time from about 4 p.m. until 11 p. m., soaking wet and throwing off my mask.
像这样的消杀要重复14天，每天背着40斤桶爬26层楼，讲不辛苦是不可能的，讲不紧张也是不现实的，但我们是专业人员，如果我们也害怕了，还怎么缓解居民的恐惧呢？有确诊病例的小区，居民肯定是恐慌的，看见我们在消毒，有时候居民就会问我们：你们的药水怎么没有味道？浓度够吗？这时候我就要跟他们解释：药水都是严格按照防疫期间疾控部门下发的环境预防性消毒技术规范配制药物浓度的，包括消毒的区域、频次都是有明确规定的，消毒这个事情马虎不得。
This is a 14-day repeat, carrying 40 kilograms of barrels a day. It is impossible to say no to hardship, and it is unrealistic to say no to stress. But we are professionals, and if we are scared, how can we alleviate the residents' fears?
听了我的解释，居民们也就越来越安心了。
As I explained it, the residents became more and more reassured.
至于我们自己，尽可能做好防护措施，穿好防护服，戴好护目镜，相信专业知识可以保护自己。
As for ourselves, do our best to protect ourselves, wear protective clothing, wear goggles, believe that professional knowledge can protect themselves.
我从2月3号复工，到现在已经快一个月了。
It is nearly a month since I returned to work on February 3rd.
平时没有发现确诊病例的时候，我们的工作主要是预防消杀——每天早上8点到岗，先预估一下今天的消杀面积，然后进行消毒液的配置，一般用的是84，1比60的比例兑纯水，一桶配备好的消毒水有30斤重，加上桶自重10斤，一共40斤。
When no confirmed cases are found, our main job is to prevent and eliminate the disease - to arrive at 8: 00 am each morning, estimate the area to be sterilized today, and then configure the disinfectant solution in a ratio of 84,1: 60 to pure water.
我们有一支队伍每天排班，9点左右我就和搭档陆玉峰背着桶出发了——1个集贸市场、6个居民小区的12个垃圾箱房及健身苑点、1个垃圾中转站、2个公共厕所，这就是我们这一组一天的工作量。
We have a team that works every day, and around 9 o'clock I set off with my partner Lu Yufeng carrying buckets - a market, 12 garbage bins and fitness points in six residential districts, a garbage dump, two public toilets, which is the workload of our group for one day.
基本上是上午打完一桶，中午回到公司吃个中饭，稍事休息后继续配置药水、出发喷洒，一天下来基本上要喷完2-3桶。
Basically a bucket in the morning, at noon back to the company to eat lunch, after a short rest to continue to dispense medicine, spray, basically at the end of the day to spray 2-3 barrels.
这个事情不能马虎，每个角角落落都要喷到位，所以一天忙完基本上太阳也要落山了。
This matter cannot be carelessly sprayed into every nook and cranny, so the sun is almost gone at the end of the day.
我的爱人是武汉人，今年春节前就回武汉去探亲了，现在还在武汉，目前身体健康。
My wife is Wuhan, before the Spring Festival to visit Wuhan this year, is still in Wuhan, the current health.
我一方面在上海做好自己的工作，一方面也牵挂武汉的亲人朋友。
On the one hand, I do my own work in Shanghai, on the one hand, I also care about relatives and friends in Wuhan.
每天晚上都和爱人视频电话聊一个小时，据她所说，武汉现在也比以前管得紧了，一方面是地毯式排查病患，一方面是封闭式管理，我听了稍微放心一点。
According to her, Wuhan, which spends an hour talking with her lover by video-phone each night, is now more tightly controlled than it used to be, on the one hand, a blanket screening of patients and, on the other hand, closed management, I am a little relieved.
像我们这样的卫生消杀员还有很多，长宁区就有180多个。
There are many sanitary disinfectors like us, and there are more than 180 in Changning District.
有人说我们也是战士，我觉得不敢当，医务人员都在前线呢，我们只是做好自己的专业工作，疫情当前，普通人也要尽一份自己的公民职责，你说对伐？征集令《新民周刊》现面向全国征集新冠肺炎采访对象和真实故事：如果你是参与抗击新冠肺炎疫情的医护人员或其家属，我们希望聆听你的“战疫”故事，也希望传达你的诉求。
Some people say we are fighters, I don't think so, medical staff are in the front line, we are just doing our professional job, and the common people are doing their civic duty.
如果你是确诊、疑似患者本人或家属，我们希望了解你和家人如何“抗疫”的过程，让外界了解你的真实经历。
If you are a confirmed, suspected patient or family member, we would like to know how you and your family have responded to the epidemic and let the outside world know about your true experience.
如果你是疫情严重地区的普通市民，我们希望展现你的乐观，并倾听你所需的帮助。
If you are an ordinary citizen of a highly affected area, we hope to show your optimism and listen to the help you need.
如果你是公共服务人员或各类捐助者，我们希望看到你的“最美逆行”，记录下你的无私。
If you are a public service provider or a variety of donors, we want to see your "most beautiful retrograde" and record your selflessness.
……抗击新冠肺炎疫情，我们诚征对疫情了解的社会各界人士，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
To fight the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic, we sincerely invite all sectors of the community to understand the epidemic, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
